<h2>Group Invitations</h2>
The links below can be distributed to users to invite them to the following groups:
<ul>
{{#group_names}}
<li>{{{group_name}}}</li>
{{/group_names}}
</ul>
<h3>General invitation</h3>
If you just want to invite people to join the groups, send them the following link:
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.assessmentgarden.org/?inv={{invitation_id}}">https://www.assessmentgarden.org/?inv={{invitation_id}}</a></li>
</ul>

<h3>Assessment-specific invitations</h3>
If you want to invite people to both join the groups and take a particular assessment, use one of the links below:
<ul>
{{#assessments}}
<li><a href="https://www.assessmentgarden.org/a?a={{assessment_id}}&inv={{invitation_id}}">{{{name}}}</a></li>
{{/assessments}}
</ul>
</div>
